Package flightsim.simconnect.data

Complex data types

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
SimConnectData The base interface for simconnect data structures.
 

Class Summary
InitPosition The InitPosition structure is used to initialize the position of the user aircraft, AI controlled aircraft, or other simulation object.
LatLonAlt The LatLonAlt structure is used to hold a world position.
MarkerState The MarkerState structure is used to help graphically link flight model data with the graphics model.
Waypoint The Waypoint structure is used to hold all the necessary information on a waypoint.
XYZ Helper class containting position of a point in three dimensionnal space
 

Package flightsim.simconnect.data Description

Complex data types

This package contains classes corresponding to complex data structures used in communication with Flight Simulator
